r, etc. are apparently counter-intuitive, but physical\nexplanations are possible if the instabilities are interpreted from wave\ninteractions perspective.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Sep 2017 19:59:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Jul 2018 22:21:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 1 Dec 2018 08:13:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-04"}
