es of the foreground visibilities\nwhere the wedge is clearly present. We illustrate our method using simulated\nLOFAR observations, finding an excellent reconstruction of the input EoR signal\nwith minimal bias.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Sep 2017 07:51:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Nov 2017 17:22:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-27"}
